      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about the atmosphere being different, but it feels like ur saying one is \"polished\" and the other is just inherently less comfortable to be in. if the crime rates are lower, why do people still associate Harlem with being \"rough\"? is it just based on the people who live there?",
